                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 171). I produce a certificate of the prisoner's conviction, at Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted, March, 1850, of stealing coats, and confined six months</hi>)—I was present at the trial—he is the same person.</p>
